generate\n4. Verify extension builds: `pnpm --filter @sireno/extension build`\n5. Verify tests pass: `pnpm --filter @sireno/extension test`\n\n### Root `package.json` Scripts (Final)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"dev\": \"pnpm -r dev\",\n    \"build\": \"pnpm -r build\",\n    \"test\": \"pnpm -r test\",\n    \"test:e2e\": \"pnpm --filter @sireno/extension test:e2e\",\n    \"lint\": \"oxlint\",\n    \"format\": \"oxfmt\",\n    \"format:check\": \"oxfmt --check\",\n    \"type-check\": \"pnpm -r exec tsc --noEmit\",\n    \"prepare\": \"lefthook install\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Files to Keep at Root\n- `README.md`\n- `CHANGELOG.md`\n- `CONTRIBUTING.md`\n- `PRIVACY.md`\n- `LICENSE`\n- `.gitignore` (updated for monorepo)\n\n---\n\nDoes this plan look good? Any adjustments before I proceed with implementation?",
