t\",\n    \"oxc\": \"latest\",\n    \"lefthook\": \"latest\",\n    \"@commitlint/cli\": \"latest\",\n    \"@commitlint/config-conventional\": \"latest\"\n  },\n  \"packageManager\": \"pnpm@latest\"\n}\n```\n\n### `pnpm-workspace.yaml`\n\n```yaml\npackages:\n  - 'packages/*'\nonlyBuiltDependencies:\n  - esbuild\n```\n\n### Files to Remove from Root (after moving)\n- `src/`\n- `public/`\n- `test/`\n- `scripts/`\n- `dist/`\n- `node_modules/`\n- `vite.config.ts`\n- `vitest.config.ts`\n- `tsconfig.json`\n- `tsconfig.node.json`\n- `tailwind.config.js`\n- `postcss.config.js`\n- `.env.development`\n- `.env.example`\n- `.env.production`\n- `package-lock.json` (npm artifact)\n- `pnpm-lock.yaml` (will regenerate)\n\n---\n\nReady to implement when you give the go-ahead!",
