max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-6 flex flex-col h-full\">\n  <div className=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto space-y-4 pb-4\">\n    {/* scrollable content */}\n  </div>\n  <div className=\"pt-4 flex justify-end\">\n    {/* sticky footer buttons */}\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n### HeroUI Color Token System\nReplace Tailwind grays with HeroUI tokens:\n- Backgrounds: `bg-content1` (main), `bg-content2`, `bg-content3`, `bg-content4`\n- Text: `text-foreground` (primary), `text-default-500` (muted), `text-default-400`\n- Borders: `border-divider`\n- Primary/Secondary: `bg-primary`, `text-primary`, `bg-secondary`, etc.\n- Foregrounds: `text-primary-foreground`, `text-secondary-foreground`\n\n## Accomplished\n\n### Completed\n1. ✅ Fixed HeroUI v2 API usage (Select, Switch, Checkbox, Slider wrappers)\n2. ✅ Added @source and @custom-variant dark to CSS files (fixed missing tab styles and dark mode)\n3. ✅ Fixed scroll layout - scrollbar at window edge, content constrained to max-w-4xl\n4. ✅ Made footer buttons sticky and right-aligned in SettingsView and SkillEditor\n5. ✅ Moved dark mode toggle from SettingsView to options navbar\n6. ✅ Restored sidepanel (permission, config, icon click behavior)\n7. ✅ Changed tabs variant to solid\n8. ✅ Fixed tab panel height to use flex-1\n9. ✅ Removed ALL custom classNames from HeroUI Navbar and Tabs components\n10. ✅ Removed custom styling from tab titles (no icon wrappers)\n11. ✅ Moved layout constraints (max-w-4xl, px-6, py-6) into individual view components\n12. ✅ Moved main app tabs from separate Tabs component into Navbar using NavbarItem + Link\n13. ✅ Changed nested tabs in InfoView and FieldsView to solid variant\n14. ✅ Created custom \"coffee\" theme with violet (primary) and amber (secondary) colors\n\n### In Progress\n**Replacing gray colors with HeroUI tokens** - Started but not completed:\n- ✅ App.tsx: Changed `bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-950` → `bg-content1`\n- ✅ Onboarding banner: Changed to use `bg-primary text-primary-foreground`\n- ⏳ Ne